\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I watched your witch Elrahet put a Spark in this dead boy\u8217\'92s body. She brought him back to life. I did not believe such a thing was possible, yet I saw it with my own two eyes. I she could infuse inanimate matter with a Spark, then perhaps she could do the same for me.\u8221\'94}
